{
  "stem": "17001.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 204.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So as I'm sitting there freezing off, I was thinking that if my sister Clara is smart, she will used the wooden shoes-- because the wooden shoes had a nails sticking out at the heel so that when you walk, you walk like you are limping.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if he-- she will use the nail from the heel of this wooden shoes, then she will able to chop up the ice.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But is easier said now than it was that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "First of all, everybody was looking if any strange movement is going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Stubenalteste were the bigger bastard you ever want to encounter with.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They-- they love to snitch on you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They love to tell bad things about you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So what happened, my sister had to watch when the Stubenalteste wouldn't watch, and nobody else was in the lavatory-- in the washroom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she kept on chopping the ice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When she came back, she gave the shoes to my sister Elizabeth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was chopping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Meantime, when I was outside, I was thinking exactly the same thing that they will do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when it-- I was praying that this should be a alarm, that the bomb should come, the plane should come.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The icy rain was coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we are sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then what happened, the [GERMAN] comes with a tremendous big heavy flashlight, like a searchlight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he's going all through the [HUNGARIAN] and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then as he is facing the light towards us, I said, dear God.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Please help me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I fainted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't know, you know-- he didn't find us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, my sister-- I mean, my-- my friend kept on saying, my dear mother, please pray for us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Help us.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I will never steal again.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
